
#######################################################################
Notes for Release 0.6
#######################################################################

*** If upgrading from 0.5 ***

Changes in the schema and bugs in the metadata table require the following procedure to be 
performed:

# mysql netdot
>ALTER TABLE Device ADD COLUMN support_contactlist integer AFTER contactlist;
>ALTER TABLE Device_history ADD COLUMN support_contactlist integer AFTER contactlist;
>delete from Meta;
>\q

From source dir:

# cd bin/
# perl insert-metadata
# perl setup-class-dbi
# cp DBI.pm /usr/local/netdot/lib/Netdot/

# restart apache

